The paper deals with the task of generating a relational table in response to a query, which involves information retrieval, database management, and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IR (Information Retrieval), followed by cs.DB (Database), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
